	<div style="text-align: left;">
	Some of the <b>username/password</b> combo <b>might not work</b>, since reviewers might have changed them while testing <br/>
	<b>Profile viewing/editing</b>: Every logged in user has the ability to change his/her profile information. Upon login, their profile is displayed, where you will also find an 'Edit' option<br/>
	
	<b>Admin - View all rooms</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'View rooms'<br/>
	<b>Admin - View (+edit/delete) a room details</b>: When in the 'View rooms', click on the 'room title' of a room to view its details. There are options to delete the room as well<br/>
	<b>Admin - Delete a room</b>: When in the 'View rooms', click on the 'Delete room' option. However, if users have booked the room, then the deletion is not permitted.<br/>
	<b>Admin - View all users</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'User List'. On the resulting page, the user has an option to filter out the user based on their user type, by clicking on the hyperlinks on the top of the page.<br/>
	<b>Admin - View user history</b>: Click on 'View history' to see the corresponding user's history.<br/>
	<b>Admin - View a user's profile</b>: When viewing all the users, click on the 'name' of the user whose profile you wish to view. <br/>
	<b>Admin - Delete a user's profile</b>: When in a user's profile, click on the Delete User option below their profile.<br/>
	<b>Admin - Create an admin</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'Add an admin' option.<br/>
	<b>Admin - Create a student</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'Add a student' option.<br/>
	<b>Admin - Create a room</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'Add a room' option.<br/>
	<b>Admin - Post an announcement (Regarding reservation endings etc)</b>: Under the 'Actions' dropdown, select 'Post an announcement' option. Select the relevant room from the dropdown<br/>

	<b>Student - View room</b>: Under 'Actions', click on 'View rooms'. This will provide a list of rooms.<br/>
	<b>Student - Room details</b>: When in 'View rooms', select the 'room title' of the room. This will lead to the room details page.<br/>
	<b>Student - Request enrollemnt</b>: In the above page, click on 'Enroll me'. <br/>
	<b>Student - Room history</b>: Under 'Actions', click "My rooms". This will provide a list of enrolled, pending and completed rooms. It can be filtered by clicking on the filter options above.<br/>
	<b>Student - Cancel a room reservation</b>: In the room above list, click on 'view' to see the student's room page. Click on the drop room option to drop the room.
